# Logs

This folder holds runtime output from the agent:

- `compliance_checks.log` — one JSON line per pre-post check (written by `scripts/compliance_check.py`)
- `raw_scrape_<date>.txt` — raw scraped policy text (written by `scripts/scrape_tiktok_guidelines.py`)
- `policy_summaries/` — summarized policy digests (create as needed)

Add `.gitkeep` or commit selectively — these files change frequently.
